Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.29,译文,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\r原文}No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:33.62,译文,,0,0,0,,敌军就在门口了\N{\r原文}The enemy is at our gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:35.39,译文,,0,0,0,,数量碾压我们\N{\r原文}Their numbers are overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.95,译文,,0,0,0,,抵挡得了一时 抵挡不了一世\N{\r原文}We will not be able to hold them back forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.37,译文,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\r原文}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.20,译文,,0,0,0,,就让致远星沦陷吗\N{\r原文}Just let Reach fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.98,译文,,0,0,0,,他们知道会发生这样的事\N{\r原文}They knew this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:47.96,译文,,0,0,0,,他们早就预见到这种结果 于是做了权衡\N{\r原文}They saw it coming, they did the math.
