Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.14,译文,,0,0,0,,没有斯巴达战士被丢下\N{\r原文}There was no Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:58.71,译文,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\r原文}He was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.98,译文,,0,0,0,,她评估了情况 做出了决定\N{\r原文}She evaluated the conditions and made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.05,译文,,0,0,0,,什么决定\N{\r原文}What decision is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.50,译文,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始我们会做决定了 我们不做选择\N{\r原文}Since when do we decide anything? We don't choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.96,译文,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们该去哪里 该怎么想 该杀谁\N{\r原文}You told us where to go and what to think, who to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.73,译文,,0,0,0,,我们每次都照做 绝不多问\N{\r原文}and we did that every time, without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.11,译文,,0,0,0,,你像士兵一样服从命令\N{\r原文}You followed orders like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.29,译文,,0,0,0,,-像机器一样  -你不是机器\N{\r原文}Like machines. - You're not a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.48,译文,,0,0,0,,那么我是什么呢\N{\r原文}What am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.03,译文,,0,0,0,,不要说人类 因为真正的人有自己的生活\N{\r原文}Don't say human, because real people have lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.50,译文,,0,0,0,,有家人\N{\r原文}They have families.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.02,译文,,0,0,0,,-有各种可能的未来  -你很伤心\N{\r原文}Possibilities. - You're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.10,译文,,0,0,0,,-我们都是  -看看她\N{\r原文}We all are. - Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.35,译文,,0,0,0,,看看她\N{\r原文}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.92,译文,,0,0,0,,-告诉我你看到了什么  -放手\N{\r原文}Tell me what you see. - Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.52,译文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你看到了什么\N{\r原文}Tell me what you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.44,译文,,0,0,0,,那是个女人还是把武器\N{\r原文}Is that a woman or a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.65,译文,,0,0,0,,那是一个人吗\N{\r原文}Is there a person in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.92,译文,,0,0,0,,还是只是你留在\N{\r原文}or is that just a piece of equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.11,译文,,0,0,0,,战场上的一件装备 扔了就扔了\N{\r原文}you leave on the battlefield, dump and forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.93,译文,,0,0,0,,他们把我们丢在那里\N{\r原文}They left us down there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.14,译文,,0,0,0,,自生自灭\N{\r原文}to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.72,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r原文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.66,译文,,0,0,0,,没有撤离计划 没有战甲\N{\r原文}No evac, no armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.25,译文,,0,0,0,,-海军情报局知道我们肯定会死  -我知道\N{\r原文}ONI knew we wouldn't make it. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.82,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星上的其他队伍呢\N{\r原文}What about the other teams on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.39,译文,,0,0,0,,有动静吗\N{\r原文}Any contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.42,译文,,0,0,0,,一片混乱\N{\r原文}It was chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.10,译文,,0,0,0,,这座城市沦陷了\N{\r原文}The city fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:49.79,译文,,0,0,0,,飞船四散奔逃\N{\r原文}Ships scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.57,译文,,0,0,0,,没有办法知道有多少人逃脱了 更不用说知道谁\N{\r原文}There's no way of telling how many escaped, let alone who- -
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.22,译文,,0,0,0,,-多久了  -我得让你进入诱导性昏迷\N{\r原文}How long have I- - ? - I had to induce a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.36,译文,,0,0,0,,-多久了  -两天\N{\r原文}How long? - Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.30,译文,,0,0,0,,-两天  -两天\N{\r原文}Two days. - Two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.68,译文,,0,0,0,,我们得回去\N{\r原文}We gotta get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.59,译文,,0,0,0,,-我们得  -约翰 别说了\N{\r原文}We gotta go- - - John, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.36,译文,,0,0,0,,-幸存者们  -约翰 约翰\N{\r原文}The survivors- - - John, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.62,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星的人们需要我\N{\r原文}People on Reach, they need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.36,译文,,0,0,0,,不 他们不需要\N{\r原文}No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.29,译文,,0,0,0,,你发烧了\N{\r原文}You have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:31.73,译文,,0,0,0,,你状态不好\N{\r原文}You're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.97,译文,,0,0,0,,我告诉了他们会发生什么\N{\r原文}I told them what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.78,译文,,0,0,0,,-好了  -我告诉他们了\N{\r原文}Come on. - I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.57,译文,,0,0,0,,我告诉艾克森了\N{\r原文}I told Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.25,译文,,0,0,0,,他们已经知道了\N{\r原文}They already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.49,译文,,0,0,0,,他们知道\N{\r原文}They knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.96,译文,,0,0,0,,他们还是什么也没做\N{\r原文}And they did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.12,译文,,0,0,0,,我本可以阻止这一切的\N{\r原文}I could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.38,译文,,0,0,0,,如果我 有战甲的话\N{\r原文}If I just...had my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.98,译文,,0,0,0,,如果她和我在一起的话\N{\r原文}If she was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.33,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星沦陷不是意外\N{\r原文}Reach wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.42,译文,,0,0,0,,是计划内的\N{\r原文}It was a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我们需要小心行事\N{\r原文}We need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.97,译文,,0,0,0,,藏起来\N{\r原文}Invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.20,译文,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\r原文}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.02,译文,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\r原文}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.25,译文,,0,0,0,,现在又是“我们”了吗\N{\r原文}it's"we"now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.54,译文,,0,0,0,,一直都是\N{\r原文}It always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道你能听到\N{\r原文}I know you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.01,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道你能看到\N{\r原文}I know you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.01,译文,,0,0,0,,你害怕了吗\N{\r原文}Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.69,译文,,0,0,0,,我召唤你\N{\r原文}I summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.89,译文,,0,0,0,,我以高等先知的名义召唤你\N{\r原文}I summon you in the name of the Hierarchs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.83,译文,,0,0,0,,众神之声\N{\r原文}voices of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:58.23,译文,,0,0,0,,下次 你可以直接按那个小按钮\N{\r原文}Next time, you can just push the little button there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.33,译文,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\r原文}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.74,译文,,0,0,0,,这是艘星盟的飞船\N{\r原文}This is a Covenant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.89,译文,,0,0,0,,这是狂徒尊者\N{\r原文}This is the command vesse
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.58,译文,,0,0,0,,瓦尔加塔奈的指挥舰\N{\r原文}of the esteemed Zealot, Var'Gatanai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.39,译文,,0,0,0,,他是庄严协议第一舰队的\N{\r原文}former Supreme Commander of the First Fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.88,译文,,0,0,0,,前最高指挥官\N{\r原文}of Solemn Accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.51,译文,,0,0,0,,神风烈士\N{\r原文}The Arbiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.75,译文,,0,0,0,,你是什么\N{\r原文}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.23,译文,,0,0,0,,我是科塔娜\N{\r原文}I am Cortana,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.55,译文,,0,0,0,,-最先进的人工智  -不\N{\r原文}the most advanced artificial- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.79,译文,,0,0,0,,你对他来说\N{\r原文}What are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:31.26,译文,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\r原文}to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.20,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长吗\N{\r原文}Master Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.20,译文,,0,0,0,,我\N{\r原文}I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.98,译文,,0,0,0,,我们一起工作\N{\r原文}We work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.33,译文,,0,0,0,,你对那个恶魔了解多少\N{\r原文}What do you know of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.81,译文,,0,0,0,,他记得你\N{\r原文}He remembers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.70,译文,,0,0,0,,你还留着他的记忆\N{\r原文}You keep his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.74,译文,,0,0,0,,给我看\N{\r原文}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.22,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}给我看看他对光环的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.25,译文,,0,0,0,,它不属于你\N{\r原文}It doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.27,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}我也不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.00,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}如果你对我来说没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.30,译文,,0,0,0,,那我对高等先知就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.75,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}你我都知道没用的东西有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.55,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}你我都知道没用的东西有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.03,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195.6,198.1)}世界上有很多种监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.09,译文,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\r原文}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.04,译文,,0,0,0,,你在说梦话来着\N{\r原文}You talk in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.38,译文,,0,0,0,,他醒了\N{\r原文}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.47,译文,,0,0,0,,嘿 哥们\N{\r原文}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.04,译文,,0,0,0,,你看起来糟透了\N{\r原文}You look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.23,译文,,0,0,0,,哈尔西在哪儿\N{\r原文}Where's Halsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.09,译文,,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\r原文}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.70,译文,,0,0,0,,你已经睡了三天了\N{\r原文}You've been out for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:57.11,译文,,0,0,0,,我试着联系站点 还是没有任何回应\N{\r原文}I tried contacting the station. Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.84,译文,,0,0,0,,她是个斗士\N{\r原文}She's a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.81,译文,,0,0,0,,我们落地后会去找她帮忙的\N{\r原文}We're gonna get her help when we get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.80,译文,,0,0,0,,-落哪儿  -阿莱利亚星\N{\r原文}Where? - Aleria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.33,译文,,0,0,0,,你听说过吗\N{\r原文}You heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.94,译文,,0,0,0,,一个废弃采矿前哨 我们几小时后就会进入轨道\N{\r原文}Busted mining outpost. We'll be orbital in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.52,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒在那儿\N{\r原文}Kessler's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.80,译文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\r原文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.53,译文,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\r原文}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.83,译文,,0,0,0,,我晚上会陪着他\N{\r原文}I stay with him at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.33,译文,,0,0,0,,每天晚上\N{\r原文}Every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.66,译文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\r原文}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.31,译文,,0,0,0,,我得去跟哈尔西谈谈\N{\r原文}I need to talk to Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.33,译文,,0,0,0,,你都不看看他的吗\N{\r原文}You're not even gonna look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.94,译文,,0,0,0,,有什么可看的\N{\r原文}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.93,译文,,0,0,0,,又不是没见过\N{\r原文}I've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.21,译文,,0,0,0,,-他是你朋友  -这不过是具尸体\N{\r原文}He's your friend. This is a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.45,译文,,0,0,0,,我朋友不在这里\N{\r原文}My friend isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.89,译文,,0,0,0,,把她放轮床上\N{\r原文}Set her on the gurney.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.65,译文,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\r原文}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.41,译文,,0,0,0,,你有无菌场发生器吗\N{\r原文}Have you got a sterile field generator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.69,译文,,0,0,0,,-我们有个手术室  -有自愈泡沫吗\N{\r原文}We have an operating room. Have you got biofoam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.09,译文,,0,0,0,,-当然有  -好 设置个创伤处理室\N{\r原文}Of course. Okay, set up a trauma station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.86,译文,,0,0,0,,准备100毫升的聚合物\N{\r原文}Prep 100 cc's of poly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.22,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你要操作器械\N{\r原文}And if you're going to be handling instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.46,译文,,0,0,0,,就给手消毒\N{\r原文}then disinfect your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.54,译文,,0,0,0,,-我才是外科医生  -今天不是\N{\r原文}- I'm the surgeon. Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.71,译文,,0,0,0,,护士 100毫升聚\N{\r原文}Nurse, 100 cc's of poly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.21,译文,,0,0,0,,还没消息\N{\r原文}Nothing yet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:15.20,译文,,0,0,0,,他们还在抢救她\N{\r原文}They're still working on her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.81,译文,,0,0,0,,里兹会没事的\N{\r原文}Riz is gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.05,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\r原文}Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:25.49,译文,,0,0,0,,我们去打听下\N{\r原文}We're gonna ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.16,译文,,0,0,0,,索伦\N{\r原文}Soren?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.14,译文,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\r原文}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.61,译文,,0,0,0,,拉挨拉等一下\N{\r原文}Laera, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.41,译文,,0,0,0,,你来不\N{\r原文}Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.31,译文,,0,0,0,,他不会离开她的\N{\r原文}He's not gonna leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.01,译文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\r原文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.22,译文,,0,0,0,,你在外面会冻死的\N{\r原文}You're gonna freeze out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:08.09,译文,,0,0,0,,是你把那破玩意儿停到外面的吗\N{\r原文}You the ones who landed that piece of shit out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.69,译文,,0,0,0,,-你好呀 朋友  -嗯 你好\N{\r原文}Howdy, friend. Yeah, howdy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.43,译文,,0,0,0,,我不想听北部山脉的事\N{\r原文}I don't wanna even hear about the northern range.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.55,译文,,0,0,0,,所有包裹都不见了\N{\r原文}All them parcels is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:21.19,译文,,0,0,0,,我在沃尔珀旧铸造厂附近找到些小的\N{\r原文}I still got some smaller pieces near the old Volper foundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.40,译文,,0,0,0,,你可能听说过土地里有毒\N{\r原文}You might have heard the ground's poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.56,译文,,0,0,0,,并没有 本该就是那颜色\N{\r原文}Well, it ain't. It's supposed to be that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.85,译文,,0,0,0,,原来就那样\N{\r原文}That's the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.27,译文,,0,0,0,,打开就得买哈\N{\r原文}You stretch it, you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:35.77,译文,,0,0,0,,算我的\N{\r原文}It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.39,译文,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你我们能做什么\N{\r原文}I'll tell you what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.48,译文,,0,0,0,,你先跟我说说你们要找什么\N{\r原文}Why don't you tell me what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.24,译文,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你去哪儿找\N{\r原文}And I'll tell you where you can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:49.48,译文,,0,0,0,,我们儿子\N{\r原文}Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:52.54,译文,,0,0,0,,-什么  -凯斯勒\N{\r原文}What now? Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.61,译文,,0,0,0,,十岁 戴个头盔\N{\r原文}He's ten years old. Wears a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.76,译文,,0,0,0,,他上了运输船\N{\r原文}He was on a transport ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.69,译文,,0,0,0,,应该是几天前落在这里的\N{\r原文}Would have landed here a couple of days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:00.62,译文,,0,0,0,,那个\N{\r原文}The, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.27,译文,,0,0,0,,博得格雷文号\N{\r原文}The Bodegraven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:05.86,译文,,0,0,0,,是 是 博得格雷文\N{\r原文}Right. Right. Bodegraven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.42,译文,,0,0,0,,这孩子\N{\r原文}And this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.18,译文,,0,0,0,,你说是你家的\N{\r原文}you say it's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:15.34,译文,,0,0,0,,我这么问是因为大多数过来的人都有主了\N{\r原文}I'm only asking, as most folks come through are spoken for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:17.29,译文,,0,0,0,,尤其是小孩子\N{\r原文}Especially little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:18.78,译文,,0,0,0,,人们很慷慨的\N{\r原文}People pay good money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:26.80,译文,,0,0,0,,权且看看吧\N{\r原文}Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.40,译文,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\r原文}Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.61,译文,,0,0,0,,最近几天热闹得很\N{\r原文}These last few days been a goddamn circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.06,译文,,0,0,0,,你听说致远星的事了吗\N{\r原文}You heard about Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:43.05,译文,,0,0,0,,-听说了  -我早就料到了\N{\r原文}Yes. - I saw it coming a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:43.93,译文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r原文}That's so..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:45.16,译文,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部根本不在乎\N{\r原文}UNSC never gave a shit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:47.34,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟入侵远地殖民地的事\N{\r原文}about the Covenant coming for the Outer Colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:50.51,译文,,0,0,0,,这帮人自食其果一点都不奇怪\N{\r原文}I shouldn't be surprised their chickens came home to roost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:53.42,译文,,0,0,0,,博得格雷文 在这里\N{\r原文}Bodegraven, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:04.94,译文,,0,0,0,,是他 博得格雷文 男孩 十岁\N{\r原文}This is him, Bodegraven. Boy, ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.30,译文,,0,0,0,,-是凯斯勒  -好\N{\r原文}This is Kessler. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:12.06,译文,,0,0,0,,我要你手上这孩子所有资料\N{\r原文}I'm gonna need everything you got on this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:23.56,译文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\r原文}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.32,0:24:26.65,译文,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\r原文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.13,0:24:30.21,译文,,0,0,0,,是时候了\N{\r原文}It's timel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:33.72,译文,,0,0,0,,干什么去\N{\r原文}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.48,0:24:38.91,译文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\r原文}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.68,0:24:41.31,译文,,0,0,0,,什么叫不\N{\r原文}What do you mean, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.73,0:24:44.03,译文,,0,0,0,,他就这么躺被单底下 我们得让他入土为安\N{\r原文}We left him lying under a sheet. We have to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:47.46,译文,,0,0,0,,-斯巴达战士是不用埋葬的  -行吧\N{\r原文}You don't bury a Spartan. - Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.51,0:24:49.80,译文,,0,0,0,,那你们怎么处理\N{\r原文}So, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:53.12,译文,,0,0,0,,-抱歉 帮不了你  -为什么不行\N{\r原文}Sorry, Ican't help you, Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:55.23,译文,,0,0,0,,你怕了\N{\r原文}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:01.23,译文,,0,0,0,,一个人成为斯巴达战士那一刻起\N{\r原文}The moment a person becomes a Spartan,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.25,0:25:03.39,译文,,0,0,0,,他们在你们世界里的生命就终结了\N{\r原文}their life in your world ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.26,0:25:06.05,译文,,0,0,0,,他们生活在我的世界里\N{\r原文}They live in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:08.61,译文,,0,0,0,,不会被埋葬\N{\r原文}There are no burials.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.63,0:25:10.55,译文,,0,0,0,,也不会有葬礼\N{\r原文}There's no funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.58,0:25:12.46,译文,,0,0,0,,他们已经道过别了\N{\r原文}They've already said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.69,0:25:19.23,译文,,0,0,0,,这也太傻了\N{\r原文}Well, that's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.03,0:25:23.07,译文,,0,0,0,,你会希望能抓住这个机会的\N{\r原文}You're gonna wish you had taken this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.78,0:25:26.28,译文,,0,0,0,,你不知道我愿意付出\N{\r原文}You have no idea what I'd give to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:35.33,译文,,0,0,0,,这样 去你的吧\N{\r原文}Know what? Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.54,0:25:36.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我自己去埋了他\N{\r原文}I'll bury him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:39.88,译文,,0,0,0,,-没区别  -对我来说有\N{\r原文}It makes no difference. - It does to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.74,0:25:45.21,译文,,0,0,0,,要把他们埋入地下 留他们在原地\N{\r原文}You put them in the ground and you leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:49.81,译文,,0,0,0,,不然他们会跟着你的\N{\r原文}Or they will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.88,0:26:16.22,译文,,0,0,0,,我捋一下哈\N{\r原文}So let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:18.49,译文,,0,0,0,,你给清理干净 然后那片土地就是你的了\N{\r原文}You gotta clean it up, but then the land is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:20.77,译文,,0,0,0,,-对 差不多吧  -不错哎 有什么条件吗\N{\r原文}Yeah, pretty much. - Nice. What's the catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:23.97,译文,,0,0,0,,-没条件  -没条件吗 跟他说呀\N{\r原文}No catch. - No catch? Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:26.91,译文,,0,0,0,,-我们不能离开 - 永远都不可以吗\N{\r原文}Well,we can't leave - Not ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.94,0:26:29.21,译文,,0,0,0,,是的 但谁会想走呢\N{\r原文}Yeah, but who'd want to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.23,0:26:31.19,译文,,0,0,0,,看看这里\N{\r原文}I mean, look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.44,0:26:34.16,译文,,0,0,0,,我为你们高兴 很美 对吧\N{\r原文}I'm happy for you. It's beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.19,0:26:36.04,译文,,0,0,0,,-别这样了  -怎么了\N{\r原文}Stop. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.53,0:26:38.24,译文,,0,0,0,,你在交朋友 欣赏风景\N{\r原文}You're making friends and enjoying the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:40.26,译文,,0,0,0,,我们在找我们的儿子 索伦\N{\r原文}We're looking for our son, Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.64,0:26:43.93,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道啊\N{\r原文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:49.94,译文,,0,0,0,,我们之前在致远星 这么多人 都死了\N{\r原文}We were on Reach. All those people. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:52.37,译文,,0,0,0,,整座城市\N{\r原文}A whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:55.89,译文,,0,0,0,,整个星球\N{\r原文}A whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.92,0:26:57.67,译文,,0,0,0,,这些都不会让你触动吗\N{\r原文}Does none of that touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.37,0:27:01.00,译文,,0,0,0,,-当然会了  -那就表现出来\N{\r原文}- Of course, it does. - Then act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.17,0:27:04.59,译文,,0,0,0,,你想我难过\N{\r原文}You want me to be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.62,0:27:06.87,译文,,0,0,0,,害怕\N{\r原文}Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.89,0:27:08.60,译文,,0,0,0,,总得有人往前看\N{\r原文}Somebody's gotta keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.63,0:27:11.18,译文,,0,0,0,,每次一出天塌了的大事 你永远都不在\N{\r原文}When things fall apart, you're never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.56,0:27:13.81,译文,,0,0,0,,你逃离了斯巴达计划\N{\r原文}You ran from the Spartan program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.83,0:27:15.54,译文,,0,0,0,,从碎石星逃出来\N{\r原文}You ran from the Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.71,0:27:17.31,译文,,0,0,0,,鲁比·安找我们的时候 就全靠我一人撑着\N{\r原文}When Ruby Ann came for us, it was all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.33,0:27:18.79,译文,,0,0,0,,等下\N{\r原文}Whoa, whoa. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.97,0:27:21.49,译文,,0,0,0,,这事你不能怪我头上\N{\r原文}You can't blame me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.51,0:27:23.92,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你在 他们会来对付我们吗\N{\r原文}Would they have come for us if you'd been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.31,0:27:29.76,译文,,0,0,0,,我确实希望你伤心 希望你害怕\N{\r原文}And I do want you to be sad and I do want you to be scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.79,0:27:33.00,译文,,0,0,0,,因为我就是这种感觉 我希望你也是一样\N{\r原文}because that's where I am and I want you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.03,0:27:43.99,译文,,0,0,0,,还有你的完美爱人\N{\r原文}♪And your perfect lover ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.01,0:27:49.00,译文,,0,0,0,,看起来像个十足的傻瓜\N{\r原文}♪Just looks like A perfect fool ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.03,0:27:51.32,译文,,0,0,0,,所以你要逃跑\N{\r原文}♪ So you go running off♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.65,0:27:54.77,译文,,0,0,0,,寻找一个完全陌生的人\N{\r原文}♪In search Of a perfect stranger ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.16,0:27:58.66,译文,,0,0,0,,而孤独\N{\r原文}♪While the loneliness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.78,0:28:01.24,译文,,0,0,0,,似乎从你生活中涌出\N{\r原文}♪ Seems to spring From your life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.93,0:28:40.39,译文,,0,0,0,,你当时就是这个表情\N{\r原文}This is exactly how you looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.21,0:28:44.71,译文,,0,0,0,,我那年14岁\N{\r原文}I was 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.56,0:28:49.68,译文,,0,0,0,,做完增强手术后醒过来\N{\r原文}I woke up after the augmentation and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.92,0:28:52.19,译文,,0,0,0,,你看向我\N{\r原文}you looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.22,0:28:54.14,译文,,0,0,0,,你还记得当时自己说了什么吗\N{\r原文}Do you remember what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:55.48,译文,,0,0,0,,眼睛\N{\r原文}Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.50,0:28:56.62,译文,,0,0,0,,往上看\N{\r原文}Look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.08,0:29:03.04,译文,,0,0,0,,三个当中活了一个\N{\r原文}"One out of three. "
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.91,0:29:07.37,译文,,0,0,0,,很多比我强的人都没能活下来\N{\r原文}Oh, so many that were better than me didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.08,0:29:11.62,译文,,0,0,0,,我们中枪\N{\r原文}We get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.69,0:29:13.90,译文,,0,0,0,,受伤\N{\r原文}We get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.17,0:29:16.76,译文,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\r原文}We get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.78,0:29:18.16,译文,,0,0,0,,再重来一遍\N{\r原文}We do it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:20.45,译文,,0,0,0,,我只会这样\N{\r原文}That's all I know how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:23.06,译文,,0,0,0,,我把一切都教给你了\N{\r原文}I taught you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.08,0:29:24.70,译文,,0,0,0,,除了如何放弃\N{\r原文}Except how to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.73,0:29:26.52,译文,,0,0,0,,我不是为了你\N{\r原文}I don't do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.04,0:29:32.20,译文,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\r原文}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.74,0:29:36.07,译文,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\r原文}I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.56,0:29:38.98,译文,,0,0,0,,但伤势太严重了\N{\r原文}But the damage is significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:42.51,译文,,0,0,0,,你没法恢复原来的状态了\N{\r原文}You won't be the soldier you once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.54,0:29:45.71,译文,,0,0,0,,你本来状态就不比从前\N{\r原文}You were already diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.57,0:29:49.20,译文,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\r原文}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.60,0:29:53.27,译文,,0,0,0,,你必须更加努力\N{\r原文}you'll have to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:38.40,译文,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么大只啊\N{\r原文}Why'd you have to be so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.98,0:30:42.19,译文,,0,0,0,,走啊\N{\r原文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.34,0:30:45.88,译文,,0,0,0,,这样如何\N{\r原文}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.20,0:30:54.70,译文,,0,0,0,,是 我也是\N{\r原文}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:03.97,译文,,0,0,0,,伤害不断累积\N{\r原文}Damage accumulates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.97,0:31:08.51,译文,,0,0,0,,她回不去以前的状态了 但时间会帮到她\N{\r原文}She won't be the same as she was, but time will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.31,0:31:12.11,译文,,0,0,0,,里兹会活下来 会再次投入战斗\N{\r原文}Riz will live and she will fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.42,0:31:15.84,译文,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都不复以往了\N{\r原文}Well, none of us are what we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.01,0:31:18.17,译文,,0,0,0,,现在我们可有可无\N{\r原文}And now we're expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.27,0:31:21.81,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星上发生的事并不是针对个人\N{\r原文}What happened on Reach wasn't personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.84,0:31:23.93,译文,,0,0,0,,甚至不是策略需要 是政治原因\N{\r原文}It wasn't even strategic. It was political.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.96,0:31:25.37,译文,,0,0,0,,是巴拉戈斯基\N{\r原文}It was Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.80,0:31:30.92,译文,,0,0,0,,是\N{\r原文}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.89,0:31:33.60,译文,,0,0,0,,事关控制权\N{\r原文}This was about control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.86,0:31:37.37,译文,,0,0,0,,事关由谁决定这场战争怎么打\N{\r原文}About who dictates how this war is fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.98,0:31:41.43,译文,,0,0,0,,她赢了\N{\r原文}She won.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.69,0:31:47.07,译文,,0,0,0,,你没法为整个星球哀悼\N{\r原文}You can't grieve an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.95,0:31:49.37,译文,,0,0,0,,太宏大了\N{\r原文}It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.39,0:31:51.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我们的思想不会让它成为现实\N{\r原文}Our minds won't let it be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.91,0:31:56.83,译文,,0,0,0,,所有这此生命 这些名字\N{\r原文}AlI those lives. All those names.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.94,0:31:59.65,译文,,0,0,0,,太多了\N{\r原文}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:03.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我要你帮我做件事\N{\r原文}I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.22,0:32:07.27,译文,,0,0,0,,我之前没机会埋葬别人\N{\r原文}I never got to bury anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.82,0:32:10.55,译文,,0,0,0,,没埋葬过我的人民\N{\r原文}Not my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.58,0:32:12.08,译文,,0,0,0,,我的家人\N{\r原文}Not my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.19,0:32:17.90,译文,,0,0,0,,不知怎么的 我需要你当所有逝者\N{\r原文}Somehow, I need you to be everyone that's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.31,0:32:21.90,译文,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\r原文}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.33,0:32:29.75,译文,,0,0,0,,取出科塔娜的人就是巴拉戈斯基\N{\r原文}Parangosky's the one who took Cortana out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:32.32,译文,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能记得这些\N{\r原文}How could you possibly have remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.34,0:32:33.55,译文,,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\r原文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.26,0:32:39.13,译文,,0,0,0,,里面有个空间\N{\r原文}There's a space inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:41.20,译文,,0,0,0,,那里曾经有个声音\N{\r原文}where there used to be a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.79,0:32:45.21,译文,,0,0,0,,我觉得有人认识我\N{\r原文}I'm feeling that somebody knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.96,0:32:48.63,译文,,0,0,0,,有些东西\N{\r原文}There was something that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.62,0:32:51.45,译文,,0,0,0,,科塔娜说\N{\r原文}Cortana said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.67,0:32:54.59,译文,,0,0,0,,就在她\N{\r原文}right before she
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.59,0:32:56.75,译文,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\r原文}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.08,0:32:59.50,译文,,0,0,0,,什么 她说了什么\N{\r原文}What? What- - What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.23,0:33:04.81,译文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选的\N{\r原文}How did you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:06.49,译文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\r原文}W- W- W- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.52,0:33:08.19,译文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选上我的\N{\r原文}How did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.34,0:33:13.92,译文,,0,0,0,,我们创建了基因档案\N{\r原文}We created the genetic profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.94,0:33:15.78,译文,,0,0,0,,-调查过所有孩子  -不是\N{\r原文}We surveyed all the children- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:20.73,译文,,0,0,0,,为什么选我\N{\r原文}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.76,0:33:27.06,译文,,0,0,0,,-我不明白  -你明白的\N{\r原文}I don't understand. Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.82,0:33:32.66,译文,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\r原文}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.16,0:33:34.53,译文,,0,0,0,,就这一次\N{\r原文}Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.86,0:33:49.70,译文,,0,0,0,,还没聊完呢\N{\r原文}We're not done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.51,0:33:57.31,译文,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\r原文}Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.79,0:34:01.08,译文,,0,0,0,,再靠近一步 我就拉你们陪葬了\N{\r原文}Come closer, I will dig another hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.31,0:34:02.81,译文,,0,0,0,,-你干什么呢  -嘿\N{\r原文}What are you doing? - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.99,0:34:04.82,译文,,0,0,0,,这帮疯子要带走他\N{\r原文}This crazy's trying to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.84,0:34:06.67,译文,,0,0,0,,你不能把他埋入地下\N{\r原文}You can't put him in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:08.68,译文,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\r原文}I beg to differ!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.70,0:34:10.61,译文,,0,0,0,,把这尸体烧了 让他去找自己的路\N{\r原文}Burn this body. Let him find his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.22,0:34:17.55,译文,,0,0,0,,-别碰他  -住手\N{\r原文}Get your hands off him! - Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.58,0:34:28.79,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\r原文}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:33.84,译文,,0,0,0,,这不是死亡\N{\r原文}This isn't death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.35,0:34:36.60,译文,,0,0,0,,这是失去\N{\r原文}This is loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.71,0:34:38.42,译文,,0,0,0,,是有区别的\N{\r原文}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.31,0:34:50.81,译文,,0,0,0,,火葬吧\N{\r原文}Put him in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.71,0:35:07.21,译文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r原文}AlI right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.14,0:35:22.85,译文,,0,0,0,,-索伦  -在\N{\r原文}Soren. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.91,0:36:04.37,译文,,0,0,0,,-什么事  -晚上好\N{\r原文}What do you want? Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.39,0:36:05.72,译文,,0,0,0,,你这叫非法闯入\N{\r原文}You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.75,0:36:08.00,译文,,0,0,0,,-容我解释  -我们是来找儿子的\N{\r原文}Allow me to explain. - We're here for our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.28,0:36:10.37,译文,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们的儿子\N{\r原文}Your what? - Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.40,0:36:11.57,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\r原文}Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.62,0:36:13.08,译文,,0,0,0,,很听话的小男孩\N{\r原文}Nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.41,0:36:15.05,译文,,0,0,0,,-差不多这么高  -他是我们的孩子\N{\r原文}Like, yay, high- - The kid is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.08,0:36:16.43,译文,,0,0,0,,鬼扯\N{\r原文}- The hell he is. -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.46,0:36:18.26,译文,,0,0,0,,冷静一点\N{\r原文}Now...let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.74,0:36:20.87,译文,,0,0,0,,去别地儿冷静去\N{\r原文}You can calm down somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.90,0:36:22.61,译文,,0,0,0,,这个家很好 他喜欢这里\N{\r原文}This is a good home and he likes it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.90,0:36:25.69,译文,,0,0,0,,要是我把他交给了两个陌生人 那我是真该死\N{\r原文}and I'll be damned if I'm giving him up to a couple of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:27.99,译文,,0,0,0,,我们不是陌生人 我们是他的父母\N{\r原文}We're not strangers. We're his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.01,0:36:31.01,译文,,0,0,0,,就算是真的 你们也不会是合格的父母\N{\r原文}Even if that were true, some parents you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.70,0:36:33.86,译文,,0,0,0,,他来到这里时 饿得半死\N{\r原文}He was half starved when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.48,0:36:36.86,译文,,0,0,0,,看上去还挨了不少揍\N{\r原文}Looked like he'd been slapped around a little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.89,0:36:38.85,译文,,0,0,0,,-你说什么  -对\N{\r原文}- What did you say? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.36,0:36:41.59,译文,,0,0,0,,我想现在知道罪魁祸首是谁了\N{\r原文}I guess we know who's responsible for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.62,0:36:42.87,译文,,0,0,0,,草 凯斯勒\N{\r原文}Fuck you! Kesslerl
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.89,0:36:45.81,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒 快出来\N{\r原文}Kessler, come out here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.15,0:36:48.31,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\r原文}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.30,0:36:51.56,译文,,0,0,0,,他就在这里 她们带走了他\N{\r原文}They have him. They took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:53.96,译文,,0,0,0,,没事的 不会有事的\N{\r原文}It's okay. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.45,0:36:57.35,译文,,0,0,0,,-冷静  -我们要怎么办\N{\r原文}Calm down. - What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.51,0:36:59.72,译文,,0,0,0,,我在呢 我能处理好\N{\r原文}I'm here. I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.08,0:37:02.54,译文,,0,0,0,,-不就是场谈判嘛  -这关系到我们的儿子啊\N{\r原文}It's a negotiation. - It's our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.55,0:37:05.89,译文,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\r原文}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.31,0:37:08.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\r原文}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.38,0:37:28.92,译文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们看上去\N{\r原文}Well, you all seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.23,0:37:31.56,译文,,0,0,0,,准备充足\N{\r原文}ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.75,0:37:34.71,译文,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道世界什么时候会崩塌\N{\r原文}You never know when the world's gonna fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.81,0:37:36.73,译文,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\r原文}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.67,0:37:41.68,译文,,0,0,0,,这茶真不错\N{\r原文}This is some really good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.80,0:37:44.80,译文,,0,0,0,,你让我们给你五分钟\N{\r原文}You said to give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.87,0:37:46.62,译文,,0,0,0,,已经过了两分钟了\N{\r原文}We already gave you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.09,0:37:51.47,译文,,0,0,0,,我小时候生活的地方和这里很像\N{\r原文}I grew up in a place just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.95,0:37:53.83,译文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\r原文}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:37:56.61,译文,,0,0,0,,意思是 我知道勉强维生是什么感觉\N{\r原文}It means I know what it is to scratch out a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.50,0:38:00.17,译文,,0,0,0,,大地产出的粮食总是达不到预期\N{\r原文}The ground never gives you what it promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.67,0:38:03.60,译文,,0,0,0,,吃的食物永远不够\N{\r原文}There's never quite enough to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:04.92,译文,,0,0,0,,我们凑合能过\N{\r原文}We get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.98,0:38:10.86,译文,,0,0,0,,我能搞来东西\N{\r原文}I'm the kind of guy that can get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.23,0:38:15.56,译文,,0,0,0,,能给予你们补偿的东西\N{\r原文}The kind of things that can compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.39,0:38:20.40,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道多一双手意味着什么\N{\r原文}I know what an extra pair of hands can mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.15,0:38:39.23,译文,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子不卖\N{\r原文}Our boy isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.64,0:38:56.48,译文,,0,0,0,,实话和你们说吧\N{\r原文}I'm gonna be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.93,0:39:01.35,译文,,0,0,0,,这里和我长大的地方完全不一样\N{\r原文}This is nothing like where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.69,0:39:05.32,译文,,0,0,0,,我出生在地狱里\N{\r原文}I was born in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.67,0:39:09.51,译文,,0,0,0,,在拳打脚踢下长大\N{\r原文}Raised in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.53,0:39:12.49,译文,,0,0,0,,没有家人 没有家\N{\r原文}Being without a family, without a home...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:17.13,译文,,0,0,0,,没有食物 没有人保护我\N{\r原文}without food, without protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.51,0:39:20.22,译文,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\r原文}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.18,0:39:25.27,译文,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\r原文}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.47,0:39:27.76,译文,,0,0,0,,我发现 我能挺过这一切\N{\r原文}I realized I can survive all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:32.07,译文,,0,0,0,,但是孤独\N{\r原文}But the loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.93,0:39:38.06,译文,,0,0,0,,要说什么能要我命\N{\r原文}If anything was gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:41.44,译文,,0,0,0,,那就是孤独\N{\r原文}it would be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:44.24,译文,,0,0,0,,真的是我\N{\r原文}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.54,0:39:47.28,译文,,0,0,0,,现在我当父亲了\N{\r原文}So now I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:48.80,译文,,0,0,0,,我生活在恐惧里\N{\r原文}And I live in fear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.02,0:39:51.52,译文,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\r原文}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.70,0:39:57.08,译文,,0,0,0,,不过我的儿子\N{\r原文}that my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.11,0:39:58.99,译文,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到那种感觉\N{\r原文}will never know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.57,0:40:04.69,译文,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到缺少爱是什么感觉\N{\r原文}That absence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.51,0:40:12.93,译文,,0,0,0,,感恩是你们收留了他\N{\r原文}I am grateful that you're the ones that took him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.62,0:40:18.87,译文,,0,0,0,,因为我知道 他迟早能在这里找到爱\N{\r原文}because I know in time, he'd find love here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.39,0:40:26.19,译文,,0,0,0,,但他是我的儿子\N{\r原文}But he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:43.23,译文,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的这个\N{\r原文}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.31,0:40:46.06,译文,,0,0,0,,一个男孩给我的\N{\r原文}A boy gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.37,0:40:48.87,译文,,0,0,0,,在运输飞船上\N{\r原文}On the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.95,0:40:51.41,译文,,0,0,0,,用来保护自己的\N{\r原文}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.24,0:40:55.49,译文,,0,0,0,,他 他发现我害怕\N{\r原文}He- - He saw that I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.09,0:40:58.51,译文,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\r原文}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:05.22,译文,,0,0,0,,被他们带走了\N{\r原文}They took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:15.47,译文,,0,0,0,,她们愿意让我们见凯斯勒了\N{\r原文}They're gonna let us see Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.25,0:41:19.54,译文,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\r原文}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.11,0:41:22.73,译文,,0,0,0,,不是凯斯勒\N{\r原文}It's not Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.07,0:41:54.57,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星不仅是一个地方\N{\r原文}Reach was more than a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.04,0:41:56.20,译文,,0,0,0,,更是一个象征\N{\r原文}It was a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.06,0:41:59.90,译文,,0,0,0,,是人类精神的丰碑\N{\r原文}It was a monument to the human spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.87,0:42:05.17,译文,,0,0,0,,纪念着牺牲了一切保卫这里的人们\N{\r原文}and to those who sacrificed everything to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.68,0:42:11.23,译文,,0,0,0,,比如雅各布·凯斯上将\N{\r原文}Those like Admiral Jacob Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.00,0:42:16.17,译文,,0,0,0,,以及这位斯巴达战士 瓦纳克·阿马迪\N{\r原文}And this Spartan, Vannak Amadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.32,0:42:20.90,译文,,0,0,0,,他在致敬星上出生\N{\r原文}He was born on Tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.08,0:42:23.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我认识他时他才六岁\N{\r原文}I met him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.82,0:42:25.62,译文,,0,0,0,,我能看得出来 他很有荣誉感\N{\r原文}I could see he had honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.67,0:42:29.09,译文,,0,0,0,,他生活在大家族里\N{\r原文}He had a large family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.11,0:42:31.45,译文,,0,0,0,,他尽忠效劳 他的家人会为他骄傲的\N{\r原文}They would be proud of his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.98,0:42:43.65,译文,,0,0,0,,他的家人在他六岁时就埋葬了他\N{\r原文}His family buried him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.01,0:42:46.56,译文,,0,0,0,,他们从来不了解他\N{\r原文}They never knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.41,0:42:52.83,译文,,0,0,0,,但我了解\N{\r原文}But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.53,0:43:05.70,译文,,0,0,0,,他的名字是瓦纳克-134\N{\r原文}His name was Vannak- 134.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.30,0:43:09.55,译文,,0,0,0,,他是个斯巴达战士\N{\r原文}He was a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.72,0:43:12.30,译文,,0,0,0,,是我们的兄弟\N{\r原文}He was our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.41,0:43:14.86,译文,,0,0,0,,他也是自己认识的唯一的亲人\N{\r原文}And the only family that he ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.60,0:43:22.77,译文,,0,0,0,,他 他这一生并不平凡\N{\r原文}This...This was not an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.54,0:43:28.76,译文,,0,0,0,,他做过的一切 付出的一切\N{\r原文}Everything that he was, everything that he gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.20,0:43:34.87,译文,,0,0,0,,永垂不朽\N{\r原文}it never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.04,0:43:51.87,译文,,0,0,0,,你的战斗没有结束\N{\r原文}Your fight is not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.65,0:43:55.66,译文,,0,0,0,,现在我会成为你的武器\N{\r原文}I will be your weapon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.75,0:44:00.46,译文,,0,0,0,,我会找到害死你的人\N{\r原文}I will find the ones who caused your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.29,0:44:02.96,译文,,0,0,0,,要了他们的命\N{\r原文}and I will end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.11,0:45:07.45,译文,,0,0,0,,你觉得你能接近巴拉戈斯基\N{\r原文}You think you can get to Parangosky?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.48,0:45:08.58,译文,,0,0,0,,接近艾克森吗\N{\r原文}To Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:10.06,译文,,0,0,0,,你连他们在哪里都不知道\N{\r原文}You don't even know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.09,0:45:11.20,译文,,0,0,0,,我会找到他们的\N{\r原文}I'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.23,0:45:12.73,译文,,0,0,0,,你只会害死你自己\N{\r原文}You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.33,0:45:17.08,译文,,0,0,0,,我没有选择你\N{\r原文}I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.57,0:45:26.32,译文,,0,0,0,,我找到了你\N{\r原文}I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.19,0:45:28.61,译文,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西打造了光环\N{\r原文}Whatever built the Halo,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.63,0:45:31.34,译文,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西留下了那些制品\N{\r原文}whatever left those artifacts behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.76,0:45:34.47,译文,,0,0,0,,它们也在你的内心留下了点什么\N{\r原文}left something in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.50,0:45:36.05,译文,,0,0,0,,你逃避不了的\N{\r原文}You can't run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.92,0:45:39.67,译文,,0,0,0,,这是你一辈子的召唤\N{\r原文}This has been calling to you your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.93,0:45:41.76,译文,,0,0,0,,这是你注定要完成的使命\N{\r原文}This is what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.89,0:45:45.54,译文,,0,0,0,,我现在只有一件事情要做 那就是找到巴拉戈斯基和艾克森\N{\r原文}The only thing I have to do is find Parangosky, Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.57,0:45:50.90,译文,,0,0,0,,约翰 你能带我们去光环\N{\r原文}John, you can take us to the Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.02,0:45:55.61,译文,,0,0,0,,我们种族能不能活下来 就看光环能教会我们什么了\N{\r原文}The survival of our species depends on what it can teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.41,0:46:00.33,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你自己去找海军情报局报仇 那就是让我们所有人陪你冒险\N{\r原文}If you go after ONI yourself, you put all of that at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.52,0:46:03.32,译文,,0,0,0,,他们不会给你留生路的\N{\r原文}They can't let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.35,0:46:10.85,译文,,0,0,0,,我已经死了\N{\r原文}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.94,0:46:24.61,译文,,0,0,0,,加入我们\N{\r原文}Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.48,0:46:27.73,译文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\r原文}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.88,0:46:32.50,译文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你\N{\r原文}Sorry, did
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.32,0:46:36.45,译文,,0,0,0,,你刚才和我说了什么吗\N{\r原文}Did you say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.07,0:46:39.95,译文,,0,0,0,,我代表星球说话\N{\r原文}I speak for the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.49,0:46:43.11,译文,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\r原文}Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.43,0:46:45.85,译文,,0,0,0,,我代表所有星球说话\N{\r原文}I speak for all the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.27,0:46:49.47,译文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r原文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.84,0:46:55.89,译文,,0,0,0,,人都去\N{\r原文}Where is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.92,0:46:57.71,译文,,0,0,0,,我代表牧歌星说话\N{\r原文}I speak for Madrigal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:03.32,译文,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\r原文}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.34,0:47:05.58,译文,,0,0,0,,我痛苦地呐喊\N{\r原文}I cry out in painl
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.61,0:47:07.57,译文,,0,0,0,,我的孩子灰飞烟灭\N{\r原文}My children are ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.97,0:47:09.71,译文,,0,0,0,,我的皮肤破裂 我的心\N{\r原文}My skin is broken. My heart- -
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.73,0:47:12.27,译文,,0,0,0,,-你是谁啊  -你是谁\N{\r原文}Who the hell are you? - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.92,0:47:20.13,译文,,0,0,0,,谁也不是\N{\r原文}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.68,0:47:23.14,译文,,0,0,0,,你是关哈\N{\r原文}You're Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.77,0:47:25.44,译文,,0,0,0,,哈氏一族最后一人\N{\r原文}Last of the Has.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.25,0:47:32.62,译文,,0,0,0,,你怎么\N{\r原文}How do you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.54,0:47:36.00,译文,,0,0,0,,-你是谁  -你背叛了我们\N{\r原文}Who are you? - You turned your back on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.33,0:47:38.75,译文,,0,0,0,,-你忘记了自己的姓名  -别过来\N{\r原文}You forgot your name. - Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.91,0:47:40.08,译文,,0,0,0,,靠近了\N{\r原文}It's close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.78,0:47:42.60,译文,,0,0,0,,-怪物  -你别过来\N{\r原文}The monster. Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.63,0:47:44.72,译文,,0,0,0,,帮助我 找到我\N{\r原文}Help me. Find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.89,0:47:47.60,译文,,0,0,0,,拯救我 解救我\N{\r原文}Deliver me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.68,0:47:49.14,译文,,0,0,0,,不要否认你的使命\N{\r原文}Do not deny your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.53,0:47:52.11,译文,,0,0,0,,-不要抛弃你的姓名  -别说了\N{\r原文}Do not forsake your name. - Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.14,0:47:53.69,译文,,0,0,0,,守护者\N{\r原文}Protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.93,0:48:00.26,译文,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\r原文}What did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.70,0:48:41.74,译文,,0,0,0,,你做了什么 我们怎么在博爱城
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.21,0:48:45.04,译文,,0,0,0,,我们的舰队被召回了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.07,0:48:47.49,译文,,0,0,0,,不 我们有任务 要去找回
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.51,0:48:51.70,译文,,0,0,0,,任务失败了 接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.72,0:48:56.39,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道他们会怎么对我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.54,0:48:57.56,译文,,0,0,0,,怎么对我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.59,0:49:00.96,译文,,0,0,0,,只能希望 他们会接受这个信物
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.03,0:49:04.03,译文,,0,0,0,,作为我失败的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.28,0:49:09.03,译文,,0,0,0,,不要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.17,0:49:11.33,译文,,0,0,0,,高等先知已经下令了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.36,0:49:13.10,译文,,0,0,0,,高等先知是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.13,0:49:18.64,译文,,0,0,0,,你再辱骂一句 我就撕碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.90,0:49:20.32,译文,,0,0,0,,先知满嘴谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.84,0:49:23.32,译文,,0,0,0,,他们根本没想着开启朝圣之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.34,0:49:26.55,译文,,0,0,0,,他们没有能力这么做 他们非天选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.58,0:49:29.96,译文,,0,0,0,,他们心知肚明 这是我们的命运 我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.44,0:49:33.07,译文,,0,0,0,,你能带领我们前往圣迹环带
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.09,0:49:37.26,译文,,0,0,0,,你拍的马屁既残忍又空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.29,0:49:40.33,译文,,0,0,0,,这些先知让你为此感到羞愧 因为他们惧怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.36,0:49:43.87,译文,,0,0,0,,他们看到了你的伟大和你纯粹的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.89,0:49:48.18,译文,,0,0,0,,他们因自己的虚伪而窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.44,0:50:29.90,译文,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.14,0:50:35.52,译文,,0,0,0,,不是我 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.55,0:50:39.63,译文,,0,0,0,,这是你的命运 你只要接受就好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.15,0:50:43.15,译文,,0,0,0,,我要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.55,0:50:49.02,译文,,0,0,0,,相信 你要相信 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.05,0:50:51.05,译文,,0,0,0,,我是世尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.74,0:50:56.76,译文,,0,0,0,,他们会派出一整支舰队来追捕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.79,0:50:59.17,译文,,0,0,0,,他们会失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.17,0:51:03.63,译文,,0,0,0,,一切早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.40,0:52:35.90,译文,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\r原文}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.69,0:52:38.86,译文,,0,0,0,,有手套吗\N{\r原文}Gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.96,0:52:41.59,译文,,0,0,0,,就在那边\N{\r原文}Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.59,0:52:50.09,译文,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\r原文}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.63,0:52:52.63,译文,,0,0,0,,你这样我没认出来\N{\r原文}I didn't recognize you with your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.46,0:52:57.26,译文,,0,0,0,,有带刺铁丝网吗\N{\r原文}Do you have any barbed wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.80,0:53:02.10,译文,,0,0,0,,那个和你一起的家伙呢\N{\r原文}Where's that, uh, fella that was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.12,0:53:03.45,译文,,0,0,0,,他想来的\N{\r原文}He wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.12,0:53:07.62,译文,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这样不太慎重\N{\r原文}But I didn't think that would be prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.87,0:53:10.12,译文,,0,0,0,,慎重\N{\r原文}Prudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.83,0:53:15.30,译文,,0,0,0,,他有点情绪化\N{\r原文}He can be a bit emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.15,0:53:20.98,译文,,0,0,0,,这种情况我看得更明白\N{\r原文}Whereas I see this kind of situation a bit more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.44,0:53:25.37,译文,,0,0,0,,-我没明白  -你肯定明白\N{\r原文}I don't think I understand. - Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.39,0:53:28.14,译文,,0,0,0,,你以前有过妈妈 对吧\N{\r原文}You had a mother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.17,0:53:29.72,译文,,0,0,0,,-对  -没有人应该挡在\N{\r原文}Yeah. - No one should come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.75,0:53:32.29,译文,,0,0,0,,妈妈和孩子之间\N{\r原文}between a mother and her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.51,0:53:34.51,译文,,0,0,0,,这个纽带很强大\N{\r原文}It's a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.11,0:53:36.73,译文,,0,0,0,,天生的\N{\r原文}Instinctive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.86,0:53:39.87,译文,,0,0,0,,我们这里来过很多孩子\N{\r原文}You know, we got a lot of kids coming through here- -
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.99,0:53:48.04,译文,,0,0,0,,几天前\N{\r原文}The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.58,0:53:50.83,译文,,0,0,0,,我在空气里闻到了一丝气味 让我回到了\N{\r原文}I caught a scent in the air, that took me back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.86,0:53:53.19,译文,,0,0,0,,我第一次给凯斯勒剪头发的时候\N{\r原文}to the first time I cut Kessler's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.78,0:53:56.16,译文,,0,0,0,,他那时还那么小\N{\r原文}He was so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.86,0:53:59.46,译文,,0,0,0,,女士 我就是个开店的\N{\r原文}Look, lady, I- I'm just a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.48,0:54:01.02,译文,,0,0,0,,他扭来扭去\N{\r原文}He was squirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.30,0:54:04.67,译文,,0,0,0,,我担心会划伤他\N{\r原文}I was nervous that I would hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.29,0:54:09.96,译文,,0,0,0,,那个时候我就知道\N{\r原文}And that's when I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.52,0:54:12.56,译文,,0,0,0,,如果谁伤害了他\N{\r原文}that if anyone ever caused him pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.58,0:54:14.70,译文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己会做出什么\N{\r原文}there's no telling what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.93,0:54:17.35,译文,,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\r原文}There would be no limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.26,0:54:25.30,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧\N{\r原文}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.32,0:54:38.68,译文,,0,0,0,,他说了吗\N{\r原文}Did he talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.71,0:54:40.63,译文,,0,0,0,,说了\N{\r原文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.81,0:54:42.60,译文,,0,0,0,,他说了凯斯勒是被谁带走的吗\N{\r原文}Did he say who took Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.65,0:54:45.99,译文,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部\N{\r原文}The UNSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.30,0:55:03.18,译文,,0,0,0,,十分钟后出发\N{\r原文}We're wheels up in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.28,0:55:07.73,译文,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\r原文}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.04,0:55:10.79,译文,,0,0,0,,-收拾一下  -我做不到了\N{\r原文}get your stuff- - - I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.88,0:55:13.38,译文,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\N{\r原文}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.97,0:55:16.43,译文,,0,0,0,,-你没事的  -我要留在这里\N{\r原文}You're gonna be fine. I'm gonna stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.15,0:55:20.98,译文,,0,0,0,,集中注意力打仗\N{\r原文}Get your head in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.84,0:55:24.01,译文,,0,0,0,,我的战争结束了 长官\N{\r原文}My fight's over, Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.54,0:55:32.55,译文,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克说结束时才结束\N{\r原文}It's over when Vannak says it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.65,0:55:33.66,译文,,0,0,0,,-凯说  -士官长\N{\r原文}When Kai says- - Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.68,0:55:35.18,译文,,0,0,0,,赢了才算结束\N{\r原文}It's over when we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.50,0:55:39.84,译文,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\r原文}On your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.58,0:55:45.75,译文,,0,0,0,,我命令你 斯巴达战士\N{\r原文}I gave you an order, Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.85,0:55:48.52,译文,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\r原文}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.57,0:56:08.36,译文,,0,0,0,,我们失去了致远星\N{\r原文}We lost Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.75,0:56:10.64,译文,,0,0,0,,我们失去了瓦纳克\N{\r原文}We lost Vannak
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.67,0:56:11.63,译文,,0,0,0,,-凯  -我知道\N{\r原文}Kai- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.65,0:56:14.52,译文,,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么做\N{\r原文}Then what are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.03,0:56:16.78,译文,,0,0,0,,我要活下去\N{\r原文}I'm going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.97,0:56:22.22,译文,,0,0,0,,你没资格说不\N{\r原文}You don't get to say no to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.39,0:56:24.72,译文,,0,0,0,,这是我们欠他们的 里兹\N{\r原文}We owe them, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.75,0:56:26.04,译文,,0,0,0,,我们失去了他们\N{\r原文}We lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.39,0:56:29.80,译文,,0,0,0,,-我失去了他们  -只是痛苦而已\N{\r原文}I lost them. It's just pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.89,0:56:32.93,译文,,0,0,0,,你能做的只有带着痛苦前行\N{\r原文}All you can do is carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.98,0:56:35.40,译文,,0,0,0,,它很沉重\N{\r原文}But it's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.29,0:56:38.83,译文,,0,0,0,,但你越不愿面对 越逃避\N{\r原文}And the more you deny it, the more you run from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.85,0:56:40.35,译文,,0,0,0,,它就会变得越沉重\N{\r原文}the heavier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.20,0:56:45.45,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你不和痛苦和解 你会被压垮的\N{\r原文}If you don't make peace with it, it will crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.13,0:56:48.92,译文,,0,0,0,,我不会让痛苦压垮我\N{\r原文}I won't let it crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.78,0:56:56.03,译文,,0,0,0,,我只有你了\N{\r原文}You're all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.25,0:57:00.62,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r原文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.16,0:57:22.83,译文,,0,0,0,,她不来了\N{\r原文}She's not coming
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.61,0:57:36.71,译文,,0,0,0,,所以，你现在谁也不是了\N{\r原文}so,you're no one now.
